(30, 1, '2017-02-23 14:37:53', '2017-02-23 14:37:53', '<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MAGNUM BOARD®</strong> is a mineral based product that will ensure your next build meets the criteria now demanded by Health Based Building project.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">A world leader, <strong>MAGNUM BOARD®</strong> is a technologically advanced, high-quality Magnesium Oxide Board (MgO Board) building material that offers superior performance in every category when compared to traditional wood fibre, gypsum and cement based products. It is homogenous – NO de-lamination. Breathability and versatility are its greatest asset. There is a product available for most applications.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''magnum-board'']', 'Magnum Board', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'magnum-board', '', '', '2017-04-02 05:15:57', '2017-04-02 05:15:57', '', 0, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/?page_id=30', 0, 'page', '', 0),
