(75, 1, '2017-02-25 04:41:24', '2017-02-25 04:41:24', '<h2 class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Wool ‘breathes’, which means a drier home, as wool absorbs and releases moisture from your living environment within a breathable construction system.</h2>\r\n<p class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Dampness is a main factor in the health risk of cold, uninsulated housing.  It is much harder to stay warm in damp air, plus the moisture can cause moulds, mildews and other organic contaminates to grow. Research shows these are a threat to your health, leading to illnesses such as asthma, bronchitis, rheumatic fever and infectious skin diseases. Terra Lana wool blend insulation is resistant to mold, unlike some other fibres often used as insulation.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''terra-lana'']', 'Terra Lana Wool Insulation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'terra-lana-wool-insulation', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:39:59', '2017-04-09 23:39:59', '', 0, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/?page_id=75', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(76, 1, '2017-02-25 04:41:24', '2017-02-25 04:41:24', '<p class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Wool ‘breathes’, which means a drier home, as wool absorbs and releases moisture from your living environment within a breathable construction system. Dampness is a main factor in the health risk of cold, uninsulated housing.  It is much harder to stay warm in damp air, plus the moisture can cause moulds, mildews and other organic contaminates to grow. Research shows these are a threat to your health, leading to illnesses such as asthma, bronchitis, rheumatic fever and infectious skin diseases.</p>\r\n<p class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Terra Lana wool blend insulation is resistant to mold, unlike some other fibres often used as insulation.</p>', 'terra lana wool insulation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-25 04:41:24', '2017-02-25 04:41:24', '', 75, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/75-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(77, 1, '2017-02-25 04:42:03', '2017-02-25 04:42:03', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Foreverbreathe Paint is a solvent-free, breathable paint for interior and exterior applications.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Comprised of plant-based chemistry, Foreverbreathe Paints give the finishing touch to any natural, breathable home. Without the nasty toxins, while competitively priced and easy to work with, this paint is an essential component for your home.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''foreverbreathe-paints'']', 'Foreverbreathe Paints', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'foreverbreathe-paints', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:40:54', '2017-04-09 23:40:54', '', 0, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/?page_id=77', 0, 'page', '', 0),
