(282, 1, '2017-04-02 05:34:31', '2017-04-02 05:34:31', 'In addition, as wool breathes it resists temperature change by absorbing and evaporating moisture from within the fibre. In a breathing construction system Terra Lana can:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Act like a very considerable thermal mass,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Resist the change in temperature,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Flatten out the peak highs and lows of temperature,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Improve the comfort of homes,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Reduce the energy required to heat and cool a home.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Terra Lana Wool Installation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'terra-lana-wool-installation', '', '', '2017-04-02 05:34:31', '2017-04-02 05:34:31', '', 0, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/?p=282', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(283, 1, '2017-04-02 05:34:31', '2017-04-02 05:34:31', 'In addition, as wool breathes it resists temperature change by absorbing and evaporating moisture from within the fibre. In a breathing construction system Terra Lana can:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Act like a very considerable thermal mass,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Resist the change in temperature,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Flatten out the peak highs and lows of temperature,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Improve the comfort of homes,</li>\r\n 	<li class="Paragraph">Reduce the energy required to heat and cool a home.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Terra Lana Wool Installation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '282-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-02 05:34:31', '2017-04-02 05:34:31', '', 282, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/282-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(284, 1, '2017-04-02 05:35:28', '2017-04-02 05:35:28', '<h2 class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Wool ‘breathes’, which means a drier home, as wool absorbs and releases moisture from your living environment within a breathable construction system.</h2>\r\n<p class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Dampness is a main factor in the health risk of cold, uninsulated housing.  It is much harder to stay warm in damp air, plus the moisture can cause moulds, mildews and other organic contaminates to grow. Research shows these are a threat to your health, leading to illnesses such as asthma, bronchitis, rheumatic fever and infectious skin diseases. Terra Lana wool blend insulation is resistant to mold, unlike some other fibres often used as insulation.</p>\r\n<p class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">[ic_add_posts category=''terra-lana'']</p>', 'Terra Lana Wool Insulation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-02 05:35:28', '2017-04-02 05:35:28', '', 75, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/75-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(285, 1, '2017-04-02 05:37:59', '2017-04-02 05:37:59', 'Terra Lana wool insulation and and Foreverbreathe wall systems work well together. This is because the unique properties of wool are allowed to work to their full potential within a breathable wall system. Click the link below to learn in more detail how wool from a sheep''s back works just as well in your walls.', 'Terra Lana', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'terra-lana', '', '', '2017-04-02 05:37:59', '2017-04-02 05:37:59', '', 0, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/?p=285', 0, 'post', '', 0),
