(373, 1, '2017-04-09 23:39:26', '2017-04-09 23:39:26', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Enhance and maintain the natural beauty of your timber surfaces with Foreverbreathe Oil Coatings.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"> Developed using innovative plant chemistry, our extensive range of natural oils, waxes and cleaning products provide exceptional performance. Being breathable and free of harmful chemicals they support a healthy home environment.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''foreverbreathe-oil-coatings'']', 'Foreverbreathe Oil Coatings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:39:26', '2017-04-09 23:39:26', '', 73, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(374, 1, '2017-04-09 23:39:59', '2017-04-09 23:39:59', '<h2 class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Wool ‘breathes’, which means a drier home, as wool absorbs and releases moisture from your living environment within a breathable construction system.</h2>\r\n<p class="Paragraph" style="text-align: center;">Dampness is a main factor in the health risk of cold, uninsulated housing.  It is much harder to stay warm in damp air, plus the moisture can cause moulds, mildews and other organic contaminates to grow. Research shows these are a threat to your health, leading to illnesses such as asthma, bronchitis, rheumatic fever and infectious skin diseases. Terra Lana wool blend insulation is resistant to mold, unlike some other fibres often used as insulation.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''terra-lana'']', 'Terra Lana Wool Insulation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:39:59', '2017-04-09 23:39:59', '', 75, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/75-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(375, 1, '2017-04-09 23:40:54', '2017-04-09 23:40:54', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Foreverbreathe Paint is a solvent-free, breathable paint for interior and exterior applications.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Comprised of plant-based chemistry, Foreverbreathe Paints give the finishing touch to any natural, breathable home. Without the nasty toxins, while competitively priced and easy to work with, this paint is an essential component for your home.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''foreverbreathe-paints'']', 'Foreverbreathe Paints', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:40:54', '2017-04-09 23:40:54', '', 77, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/77-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(376, 1, '2017-04-09 23:41:17', '2017-04-09 23:41:17', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Using timber in construction can be very unsustainable, or in the case of Foreverbeech™, very sustainably.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">It can also be very unhealthy when treated with toxic chemicals for durability, or in the case of Foreverbeech, durable in itself and no requirement for chemical treatments.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">New Zealand beech harvested from the West Coast of New Zealand by industry-leading firm New Zealand Sustainable Forestry Products (NZSFP), is the number one option for sustainably sourced hardwood. It''s forest management practices are second to none, as documented by the United Nations Food and Agriculture Organisation (<a href="http://www.fao.org/docrep/007/ae542e/ae542e00.htm">click here</a>), Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry (<a href="http://www.foreverbeech.co.nz/app_docs/confirmation_of_sustainable_forest_mngmt_maf_2010-05-11.pdf">click here</a>) and Ministry of Primary Industries (MPI).</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''foreverbeech'']', 'Foreverbeech', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '79-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:41:17', '2017-04-09 23:41:17', '', 79, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/79-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(377, 1, '2017-04-09 23:41:42', '2017-04-09 23:41:42', '<h2 class="fl-heading" style="text-align: center;">Laminated Veneer Lumber is an engineered wood product that provides a consistent, high-performance alternative to solid lumber and steel in structural uses.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Nelson Pine operates one of the largest and most modern LVL production lines in the Asia Pacific region. See below a short video of Nelson Pine''s modern LVL production line.</p>\r\n[ic_add_posts category=''lvl'']', 'LVL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '82-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-09 23:41:42', '2017-04-09 23:41:42', '', 82, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/82-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
