(471, 2, '2017-06-01 20:44:03', '2017-06-01 08:44:03', '<p class="fl-heading"><strong><span class="fl-heading-text">Our Purpose</span></strong></p>\nPurity Homes was formed in 2011 with the purpose of providing you with an easy way to design and build a healthy home, without a big price tag. Most homes in New Zealand, old and new, are mouldy and toxic boxes. We are here to change that. You now have the opportunity to live in a home that truly puts your health first. And we make the process simple and quick!\n\n.\n<p class="fl-heading"><strong><span class="fl-heading-text">Our Vision</span></strong></p>\nOur vision is not only for New Zealand, but for a world where everyone lives in a healthy home made from non-toxic and natural materials. We imagine a world where all building materials are renewable and have waste-stream management plans. A world where homes and offices look after the health and pockets of their occupants, and the wellbeing of nature.\n<p class="fl-heading"> <strong><span class="fl-heading-text">Background and Development</span></strong></p>\nOur team was formed out of mutual interest in creating something good, something meaningful and something which adds social value. It did not take long after the Christchurch earthquakes for us to identify that the rebuild provided opportunities for improving the NZ housing stock. With the combination of Guido’s upbringing in The Netherlands and Drew’s knowledge of the NZ building industry, it only took one or two discussions to decide that NZ needed some good energy put into bettering the health and performance of buildings. Thus Purity Homes was formed.\n\nAfter three years of worldwide research we joined forces with the developers of ForeverBreathe products and systems. Captivated by the ForeverBreathe teams’ shared energy and passion, we soon found ourselves tangled in the web of breathable building systems. Purity Homes has now secured a solid business model to deliver our core values and vision into NZ by enabling kiwis to design and build with a full Health Based building system.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '387-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-06-01 20:44:03', '2017-06-01 08:44:03', '', 387, 'http://www.purityhomes.co.nz/387-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
